<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This might sound old school, but cleanliness in the locker room is a reflection of team pride. I’ve worked with enough teams to see the difference it makes when a team takes their locker room seriously. A clean, well-organized locker room fosters a sense of respect – for the team, the facilities, and each other.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
